	<description>
		JoomlaWatch is an AJAX component and module for Joomla CMS that allows you to watch
		your website visitors and bots in real-time from the administration menu. Specially 
		their IP addresses, countries they come from, which pages they are viewing, their 
		browser and operating system, it creates daily and all-time stats from these 
		information plus unique, pageload and total hits statistics. Furthermore, you can 
		block harmful IP addresses and see blocked attempts stats.
	</description>
